      "value": "\n                <i>You are adept at guiding your mount through combat.</i>\n                <br />\n                <br />\n                \n                <p><b>Prerequisites</b></p>\n                <p> Ride 1 rank.</p>\n                \n            <br />\n                <p><b>Benefits</b></p>\n                <p><p class=\"stat-block-1\"> Once per round when your mount is hit in combat, you may attempt a Ride check (as an immediate action) to negate the hit. The hit is negated if your Ride check result is greater than the opponent's attack roll.</p></p>\n                \n            \n            "
